#. type: deffn
#: original_texis/os.texi:2132
msgid "In most cases, @var{repeat} has no effect on when @emph{first} call takes place---@var{time} alone specifies that.  There is one exception: if @var{time} is @code{t}, then the timer runs whenever the time is a multiple of @var{repeat} seconds after the epoch.  This is useful for functions like @code{display-time}."
